OL,3,CIsle of Man nurses 'prepared to
OL,4,Cstrike' over Manx Care 4% pay offer
OL,6,FThis was the third offer that has been
OL,7,Fmade for this pay period and previous
OL,8,Foffers were rejected by staff side.
OL,10,FThe RCN was left concerned that the
OL,11,Foffer did not include back-pay for
OL,12,Fthose who had already left Manx Care
OL,13,Fin the months since the offer should
OL,14,Fhave been implemented and challenged
OL,15,FManx Care on this matter.
