OL,3,CIsle of Man nurses 'prepared to
OL,4,Cstrike' over Manx Care 4% pay offer
OL,6,FThe RCN North West regional board, TU
OL,7,FCommittee and Council agreed that a
OL,8,Findicative ballot asking members
OL,9,Fworking for Manx Care if they would be
OL,10,Fwilling to take strike action would
OL,11,Ftake place following the rejected
OL,12,Foffer in November.
OL,14,FThe survey ran from midday on
OL,15,FWednesday 26 February 2025 until
OL,16,Fmidday on Wednesday 12 March 2025.
