OL,6,F'Manx Care is responsible for pay
OL,7,Fnegotiations with Manx Pay Terms and
OL,8,FConditions/National Joint Council
OL,9,F(MPTC/NJC) group of staff which
OL,10,Fincludes Nurses, Allied Health
OL,11,FProfessionals, Social Care staff, non-
OL,12,Fregistered health and care staff and
OL,13,Fthose in health and care supporting
OL,14,Froles. There are nine trade unions
OL,15,Frepresented within MPTC/NJC group,
OL,16,Fincluding the Royal College of Nursing.
