OL,3,CIsle of Man nurses 'prepared to
OL,4,Cstrike' over Manx Care 4% pay offer
OL,6,F'In September 2024, Manx Care offered
OL,7,Fa 4% pay offer to all MPTC/NJC via the
OL,8,Fjoint negotiating arrangements. All
OL,9,Ftrade unions then balloted this offer
OL,10,Fin October and November 2024 and seven
OL,11,Faccepted. In December 2024, the Royal
OL,12,FCollege of Nursing (RCN) and the Royal
OL,13,FCollege of Midwives (RCM) rejected the
OL,14,Foffer. Manx Care held detailed
OL,15,Fdiscussions with staff side each month
OL,16,Ffollowing this. In February 2025, Manx
OL,17,FCare took the decision to impose the
OL,18,Foffer on the basis that seven of the
OL,19,Fnine unions had accepted it, and
OL,20,Fmindful of our funding constraints.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
