OL,3,CIsle of Man nurses 'prepared to
OL,4,Cstrike' over Manx Care 4% pay offer
OL,6,F'In February 2025, the RCN advised
OL,7,FManx Care they would be conducting an
OL,8,Findicative ballot on industrial
OL,9,Faction, and in March 2025 they
OL,10,Fconfirmed the outcome of this ballot.
OL,11,FWhilst the indicative ballot shows
OL,12,Fsupport for industrial action from the
OL,13,Fmembership who voted, in line with the
OL,14,FTrade Unions Act 1991, this is not a
OL,15,Fformal ballot for strike action, and
OL,16,FManx Care remains committed to
OL,17,Fexploring alternatives in the
OL,18,Fworkplace.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
