OL,3,CIsle of Man nurses 'prepared to
OL,4,Cstrike' over Manx Care 4% pay offer
OL,6,F'The RCN has advised Manx Care they
OL,7,Fare available for meetings to resolve
OL,8,Fthe dispute, and Executives from Manx
OL,9,FCare held an initial meeting with RCN
OL,10,Frepresentatives on 17 March. Further
OL,11,Fmeetings are scheduled. The purpose of
OL,12,Fthese meetings is to understand what
OL,13,Fthe RCN is seeking in terms of
OL,14,Fsatisfactory settlement.
OL,16,F'To date the RCM have not advised Manx
OL,17,FCare of any next steps following their
OL,18,Fmembers rejection of the pay deal.'
